asset.hookText: Skin-care Guru Kate Somerville discusses how she prepares A-list celebrities to walk the red carpet with glowing skin. Kate's secret beauty weapons include laser treatments Pearl and Titan to reduce wrinkles and fine lines, as well as tighten and polish the skin.
